Build a Query for an Endpoint

Source: R/query_build.R
build.Rd

Build a Query for an Endpoint

Usage

build(obj, qry)

Arguments

obj

An <endpoint>, <collection> or <group> object.

qry

A <query> object.

Value

A list of query parameters matched to an endpoint's fields.

Examples

qry <- new_query(
   first_name  = starts_with("An"),
   middle_name = ends_with("e"),
   last_name   = contains("J"),
   state       = any_of(c("CA", "GA", "NY")),
   year        = 2021:2025,
   practice_state_or_us_territory = any_of(c("CA", "GA", "NY")))

build(endpoint("enroll_prov"), qry)
